00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
No bit of misery or cruelty meted out to you

268
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Gives me any peace.

269
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Why do I only grow more restless?

270
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
You're responsible for all that's happening,

271
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
And I can't take it anymore.

272
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I want an end to this, Reham.

273
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I can only end it one way.

274
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Kill the one who's responsible.

275
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I'm not so weak and heartless as you

276
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
That I'd kill another human.

